Class SimpleMarkerSymbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.symbology.fmap.mapcontext.rendering.symbol.impl.AbstractCartographicSupport

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, CartographicSupport, IPrintable, ISymbol, ISymbol_v2, IMarkerSymbol, IMarkerSymbol_v2, ISimpleMarkerSymbol, Persistent

    public class SimpleMarkerSymbol
extends AbstractMarkerSymbol
implements ISimpleMarkerSymbol
    SimpleMarkerSymbol is the most basic symbol for the representation of point objects which can define its size and color apart from the rotation and the offset from a point in the map.
